" {TEXT 263 23 "Algebraic Manipulations" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 
"" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 179 "Save your current worksheet as work
02-yourlastname.mws.  Remember to save frequently to avoid losing data
 in case that the system would shut down in the middle of a work sessi
on! " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 104 "
In the text mode (click on the cap T button) place your name(s) and da
te at the top of your worksheet.  " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}
{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 531 "1.  Basic Manipulations.  We can use Map
le to manipulate algebraic expression as well as to perform arithmetic
 calculations.  The intent is to learn some basic Maple syntax, while \+
observing some of the neat features of a Computer Algebra System (CAS)
.  We will also review some basic concepts from arithmetic.   Perform \+
the following calculations with Maple.  As you do these exercises ente
r notes and comments onto your worksheet in text mode.  Note the usage
 of operators +,-,*,/,^,!  and the usage or non-usage of parentheses. \+
 " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 60 "Let \+
the following variables represent algebraic expressions:" }}{PARA 0 "
" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 6 "1.    " }{XPPEDIT 
19 1 "f := x^3-x^2-2*x" "6#>%\"fG,(*$%\"xG\"\"$\"\"\"*$F'\"\"#!\"\"*&F
+F)F'F)F," }{TEXT -1 1 " " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "
" 0 "" {TEXT -1 10 "     2.   " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "g := 6*x^3+11*x^2+6*x+
1" "6#>%\"gG,**&\"\"'\"\"\"*$%\"xG\"\"$F(F(*&\"#6F(*$F*\"\"#F(F(*&F'F(
F*F(F(F(F(" }{TEXT -1 22 "                 3.   " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "h :=
 x^3-5*x+x^2-5;" "6#>%\"hG,**$%\"xG\"\"$\"\"\"*&\"\"&F)F'F)!\"\"*$F'\"
\"#F)F+F," }{TEXT -1 19 "                   " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT 
-1 6 "4.    " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "F := x^4-1" "6#>%\"FG,&*$%\"xG\"\"%\"\"
\"F)!\"\"" }{TEXT -1 22 "                5.    " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "G := \+
3*x^4+4*x^3-2*x^2+x-6;" "6#>%\"GG,,*&\"\"$\"\"\"*$%\"xG\"\"%F(F(*&F+F(
*$F*F'F(F(*&\"\"#F(*$F*F/F(!\"\"F*F(\"\"'F1" }{TEXT -1 14 "         6.
   " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "H := 2*x^2+3*x-2" "6#>%\"HG,(*&\"\"#\"\"\"*$%\"xG
F'F(F(*&\"\"$F(F*F(F(F'!\"\"" }{TEXT -1 24 "                        " 
}}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 49 "Calcuat
e the following (each on a separate line):" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT 
-1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 123 "a.   f*g                      \+
 b.   g*(h-f)                  c.   f^3                 d.  (f + g)*(f
 - h) + (f - g)*(f + h)" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 141 "e.  F*H/G    \+
              f.   (F/H)/G                 g.  F/(H/G)           h.   \+
 F/H*G                                        i.   F/(H*G)" }}{PARA 0 
"" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 17 "f :=
 x^3-x^2-2*x;" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#>%\"fG,(*$)%\"xG\"\"$
\"\"\"F**$)F(\"\"#F*!\"\"*&F-F*F(F*F." }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" 
{MPLTEXT 1 0 25 " g := 6*x^3+11*x^2+6*x+1;" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" 
{XPPMATH 20 "6#>%\"gG,**&\"\"'\"\"\")%\"xG\"\"$F(F(*&\"#6F()F*\"\"#F(F
(*&F'F(F*F(F(F(F(" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 19 "h := x
^3-5*x+x^2-5;" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#>%\"hG,**$)%\"xG\"\"$
\"\"\"F**&\"\"&F*F(F*!\"\"*$)F(\"\"#F*F*F,F-" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 
0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 12 " F := x^4-1;" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#
>%\"FG,&*$)%\"xG\"\"%\"\"\"F*F*!\"\"" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" 
{MPLTEXT 1 0 27 "G := 3*x^4+4*x^3-2*x^2+x-6;" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" 
{XPPMATH 20 "6#>%\"GG,,*&\"\"$\"\"\")%\"xG\"\"%F(F(*&F+F()F*F'F(F(*&\"
\"#F()F*F/F(!\"\"F*F(\"\"'F1" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 
