inear factors.  What is the difference?  Some of the factors may invol
ve complex roots rather than real roots.  For example compare:" }}
{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 
